                  You must be at least 18 years old to use our services. By using the Platform, you represent and warrant that you are at least 18 years of age and have the legal capacity to enter into these terms.
                </p>
              </div>

              <!-- 3. Account Registration -->
              <div>
                <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">3. Account Registration</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
                  To use certain features of the Platform, you must register for an account. You agree to provide accurate and complete information during registration and to keep your account information updated.
