                <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-300 space-y-2 ml-4">
                  <li>You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your account credentials</li>
                  <li>You must notify us immediately of any unauthorized use of your account</li>
                  <li>We reserve the right to suspend or terminate accounts that violate our terms</li>
                </ul>
              </div>

              <!-- 4. Services and Games -->
              <div>
                <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">4. Services and Games</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
                  We provide various online games and gaming services. By using our services, you agree to:
                </p>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-300 space-y-2 ml-4">
                  <li>Play games fairly and in accordance with the rules</li>
                  <li>Not use any automated systems or bots</li>
                  <li>Not engage in any form of cheating or manipulation</li>
                  <li>Not use multiple accounts or share accounts with others</li>
                </ul>
              </div>

              <!-- 5. Payments and Transactions -->
              <div>
                <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">5. Payments and Transactions</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
                  All transactions on the Platform are subject to the following terms:
