                <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-300 space-y-2 ml-4">
                  <li>All payments must be made through approved payment methods</li>
                  <li>We reserve the right to verify any transaction</li>
                  <li>Withdrawals are subject to verification and processing time</li>
                  <li>We may charge fees for certain transactions</li>
                </ul>
              </div>

              <!-- 6. User Conduct -->
              <div>
                <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">6. User Conduct</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
                  Users must not:
                </p>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-300 space-y-2 ml-4">
                  <li>Use the Platform for any illegal purposes</li>
                  <li>Harass, abuse, or harm other users</li>
                  <li>Attempt to manipulate game outcomes</li>
                  <li>Use the Platform to promote other services without permission</li>
                </ul>
              </div>

              <!-- 7. Intellectual Property -->
              <div>
                <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">7. Intellectual Property</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
                  All content, games, and materials on the Platform are protected by intellectual property rights. Users may not copy, modify, or distribute any content without our permission.
